\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10686843 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 
Yes. But if it was something that you needed you - got it. Or - instead if you didn't need anything then you got perhaps a bigger doll or a box of - dolls furniture or a big box of dolls cups and saucers and we used to play for hours with the -
