\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818  her Lady Winifred Hope. Yes. And nobody would really believe they used to think that she was - she was taking the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8159037\charrsid814818 Mickey}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818  out of them and I remember me - mother tell
ing us that - she stood for one of her sisters and that to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1069797 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 
 and when the - she went - they went to sign the register - Lady Winifred Hope - the priest thought she'd gone mad.
