i
l her mother brought her back and told me mother - I give her a real black eye. That must have been the last punch. And me mother's going to cotter me for doing that and me father happened to come in and he'd a bit about of it and me father stopped her. H
e
 said, oh no, he said, you don't do that he said. She's won on her own he said, she's got to get her back to the wall - she's got to fight for herself if they - if they hit her well she's got to hit back, he says, and don't you hit her - for it. To me mot
her. And of course it caused a few words between me mother - but he made me mother see sense. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8396337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 Was it always your mother who punished you?
\par 
