d for nearly a - as week. But - there was - a bit of madness in it because I used to cry hard and I know if I cried hard well he used to - give me more - always give me something to spend. So I was a bit crafty that way. He was very soft but me mother was
n't. Oh no, mother was - mother was really stricter than me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8396337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your sister in a certain way?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10686843 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 
