thing wrong or anything that wasn't right we had to go upstairs - we were sent upstairs to bed. Yes. But I always remember me sister - me sister - even in them days when she was only perhaps five or six - and if she was sent upstairs she'd get undressed a
nd go to bed but I wouldn't - I used to come and sit at the top of the stairs and there used to be like a - a banister - not a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8159037\charrsid814818 banister}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
