Well I was like - a general - my mob when I first went there was cleaning the shop and polishing the fixtures - counter - and seeing to the fitting room where the ladies used to go and be fitted, see, that was all tided and polished and everything. 
And if any lady come in to go into the shop and ask them, they used to be strict times for fittings, you know, they'd be given a time to come in and then of course it that - that was done and they were pretty slack I used to eyelet - what they call eyelet
 the corsets.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8396337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818 What was this?
