\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8159037\charrsid814818 in-between}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14037617\charrsid814818  - the corsets you see at that time. And -
